    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to get this absolute beauty into the hands of a new owner. Honestly, she is in flawless condition\u2014kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family! It still smells brand new inside and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for that 'fresh off the lot' feel without the new-car price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
