    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with razor-sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a pristine subframe and documented VANOS maintenance, ensuring optimal valve timing and mechanical longevity. The Getrag six-speed manual linkage is tight and precise, delivering power to the rear wheels through a perfectly calibrated M-variable differential lock. Every body panel retains its original factory VIN sticker, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing deflection. This is a mechanically superlative specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
