      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous care, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically, it operates with the precision of a new machine, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for excellence. This is a rare acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands a showroom-quality asset.",
