      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and kept it tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 45500.0,
